memory:
T1: Primary tumor size is 2 cm or less
T2: Primary tumor size is greater than 2 cm and up to 5 cm
T3: Primary tumor size is greater than 5 cm
T4: Primary tumor of any size with direct extension to the chest wall and/or skin
T stage is determined by the size of the primary tumor, not including the DCIS (ductal carcinoma in situ) component
